  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297776</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>やめて！
どうしてエトをいじめるの！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Just stop it! Why do you insist
on tormenting Eto like this!? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297868</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こいつなんかヘンなのら～
調べるのら～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This thing's weird! I gotta examine it more!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>297936</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エトをはなせ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hand Eto over now!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はなさない～
はなさないのら～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not giving! Not giving it to you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298100</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……どうしよう……
ねぇ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why...did it come to this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298216</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>泣かないの。
私も一緒にあのわからずやさん、
ぶっ叩いてあげるから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't cry! Together we'll give this obstinate
jerk a lesson he'll never forget!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>乱暴な選択だが、
彼らの気を鎮めるには
そうする他ないかもな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's a pretty violent approach. However, given who we're
dealing with, I don't think there's much of a choice.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>298412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_070_030_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>じゃあ、行くぜ……
覚悟しろ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And now...get ready! Here we go!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
